flowchart LR
  DT[Discord text] --> Tool[minecraft_task]
  DV[Discord voice] --> Tool
  Tool --> Session[MinecraftSession]
  Chat[Minecraft chat events] --> Session
  Session --> Brain[Minecraft brain]
  Brain --> Decision[High-level command or chat/action decision]
  Decision --> Exec[Deterministic session executor]
  Exec --> MCP[Minecraft MCP server]
  MCP --> Mineflayer[Mineflayer bot]
  Mineflayer --> World[Minecraft server]
  MCP --> Snapshot[World state and event snapshots]
  Snapshot --> Session
